WEBVTT

STYLE
::cue {
font-size: 1em;
font-weight: bold;
color: #ffffff;
}

00:01:31.180 --> 00:01:34.700 line:80%
=Generation to Generation=

00:01:34.820 --> 00:01:37.700 line:80%
=Episode 26=

00:01:45.180 --> 00:01:46.020 line:80%
Stop!

00:01:49.290 --> 00:01:50.130 line:80%
Zhao,

00:01:50.130 --> 00:01:50.970 line:80%
move aside.

00:01:52.370 --> 00:01:53.210 line:80%
Zhao.

00:01:53.340 --> 00:01:54.300 line:80%
What are you doing here?

00:01:55.060 --> 00:01:56.620 line:80%
Master, don't kill him.

00:02:00.180 --> 00:02:01.020 line:80%
Wenxun,

00:02:01.340 --> 00:02:02.180 line:80%
put down the sword.

00:02:08.650 --> 00:02:09.690 line:80%
No need to say anything.

00:02:11.090 --> 00:02:11.930 line:80%
I trust you.

00:02:12.490 --> 00:02:13.330 line:80%
Leave now.

00:02:21.690 --> 00:02:22.530 line:80%
Mu Qingyan.

00:02:23.460 --> 00:02:24.300 line:80%
Mu Qingyan.

00:02:35.930 --> 00:02:36.770 line:80%
Zhao,

00:02:49.490 --> 00:02:50.410 line:80%
I thought

00:02:52.930 --> 00:02:54.570 line:80%
I'd never see you again.

00:02:54.580 --> 00:02:59.490 line:80%
♪Would there be no longing♪

00:03:00.570 --> 00:03:02.760 line:80%
♪In that fleeting moment♪

00:03:03.530 --> 00:03:06.100 line:80%
♪Within this lifetime♪

00:03:06.370 --> 00:03:07.210 line:80%
Go.

00:03:07.230 --> 00:03:12.130 line:80%
♪We already brushed past
countless times♪

00:03:12.140 --> 00:03:12.980 line:80%
Zhao,

00:03:14.970 --> 00:03:15.860 line:80%
I didn't lie to you.

00:03:17.900 --> 00:03:19.210 line:80%
That wasn't my father.

00:03:20.270 --> 00:03:22.560 line:80%
♪Love and hate, scattered in threads♪

00:03:22.560 --> 00:03:26.860 line:80%
♪Intertwined and tangled into lines♪

00:03:28.340 --> 00:03:29.460 line:80%
Stop your lies!

00:03:29.460 --> 00:03:33.520 line:80%
♪Life spreads without boundary♪

00:03:33.800 --> 00:03:36.270 line:80%
♪After parting♪

00:03:36.370 --> 00:03:37.210 line:80%
Stop!

00:03:37.210 --> 00:03:39.000 line:80%
♪Before death♪

00:03:39.060 --> 00:03:40.650 line:80%
What exactly do you want?

00:03:41.490 --> 00:03:42.740 line:80%
This has nothing to do with him.

00:03:43.930 --> 00:03:44.770 line:80%
Let him go.

00:03:54.410 --> 00:03:55.250 line:80%
Master,

00:03:55.460 --> 00:03:56.370 line:80%
please let him go.

00:03:56.620 --> 00:03:57.460 line:80%
What are you doing?

00:03:57.780 --> 00:03:58.620 line:80%
Get up.

00:03:58.620 --> 00:04:00.340 line:80%
Please, Master.

00:04:00.650 --> 00:04:02.090 line:80%
Zhao, what are you doing?

00:04:02.900 --> 00:04:03.740 line:80%
Zhao,

00:04:04.930 --> 00:04:06.060 line:80%
don't beg him.

00:04:06.282 --> 00:04:07.970 line:80%
He's the Young Master
of the demonic sect.

00:04:07.970 --> 00:04:09.180 line:80%
I can't release him.

00:04:09.810 --> 00:04:10.900 line:80%
Don't beg him.

00:04:14.140 --> 00:04:14.980 line:80%
- Don't.
- Zhao.

00:04:15.850 --> 00:04:16.700 line:80%
Don't go over there.

00:04:20.850 --> 00:04:21.690 line:80%
Let me go.

00:04:25.000 --> 00:04:27.170 line:80%
♪In dreams♪

00:04:27.720 --> 00:04:29.650 line:80%
♪I become a sleeping lotus♪

00:04:29.730 --> 00:04:30.570 line:80%
Zhao.

00:04:31.490 --> 00:04:33.680 line:80%
♪Before awakening♪

00:04:33.940 --> 00:04:37.580 line:80%
♪I have already lost sleep♪

00:04:38.000 --> 00:04:40.440 line:80%
♪Love and hate, scattered in threads♪

00:04:40.440 --> 00:04:44.660 line:80%
♪Intertwined and tangled into lines♪

00:04:45.150 --> 00:04:47.010 line:80%
♪With sandstorms filling the sky♪

00:04:47.010 --> 00:04:50.140 line:80%
♪I can still recognize your face♪

00:04:50.260 --> 00:04:51.170 line:80%
You...

00:04:51.170 --> 00:04:52.010 line:80%
Zhao!

00:04:52.140 --> 00:04:53.140 line:80%
Put down the sword!

00:04:55.850 --> 00:04:56.690 line:80%
Master,

00:04:57.850 --> 00:04:59.500 line:80%
will you release him or not?

00:05:03.770 --> 00:05:11.000 line:80%
♪I only wish to remember your face♪

00:05:18.650 --> 00:05:19.490 line:80%
Zhao,

00:05:20.530 --> 00:05:21.610 line:80%
you can't save him.

00:05:30.380 --> 00:05:31.700 line:80%
(We love without doubt)

00:05:31.940 --> 00:05:33.460 line:80%
Pingshu's hairpin.

00:05:45.650 --> 00:05:47.650 line:80%
Take Mu Qingyan into custody first.

00:05:48.290 --> 00:05:49.780 line:80%
Assign guards to watch him.

00:06:05.850 --> 00:06:08.410 line:80%
When the stars and moon are at peace,
and the world is calm,

00:06:09.650 --> 00:06:10.940 line:80%
the wedding will proceed at once.

00:06:11.500 --> 00:06:12.770 line:80%
Cai Pingshu.

00:06:14.810 --> 00:06:15.730 line:80%
Mu Zhengyang.

00:06:17.460 --> 00:06:18.460 line:80%
Who is Mu Zhengyang?

00:06:19.340 --> 00:06:20.900 line:80%
Hair intertwined,

00:06:21.900 --> 00:06:23.900 line:80%
(Cai Pingshu, Mu Zhengyang)
we love without doubt.

00:06:28.530 --> 00:06:30.140 line:80%
I see.

00:06:30.500 --> 00:06:31.340 line:80%
Zhou,

00:06:32.290 --> 00:06:33.900 line:80%
you can't blame Pingshu for this.

00:06:34.610 --> 00:06:37.380 line:80%
She met him after your betrothal
was broken.

00:06:38.140 --> 00:06:39.170 line:80%
At first,

00:06:39.170 --> 00:06:41.410 line:80%
when Mu appeared,

00:06:42.020 --> 00:06:43.770 line:80%
he looked refined and proper,

00:06:44.700 --> 00:06:45.780 line:80%
with profound cultivation

00:06:46.290 --> 00:06:47.860 line:80%
and a bold, carefree nature.

00:06:48.610 --> 00:06:50.210 line:80%
Even I felt

00:06:50.210 --> 00:06:52.020 line:80%
he was worth befriending.

00:06:52.020 --> 00:06:53.020 line:80%
However...

00:06:54.850 --> 00:06:55.690 line:80%
Zhou,

00:06:56.140 --> 00:06:57.780 line:80%
it has been a long time.

00:06:58.610 --> 00:06:59.650 line:80%
Dwelling on it is useless.

00:07:01.820 --> 00:07:02.700 line:80%
How about

00:07:02.720 --> 00:07:04.170 line:80%
we discuss the present?

00:07:04.170 --> 00:07:05.090 line:80%
It seems

00:07:05.110 --> 00:07:06.500 line:80%
the skin-painted demon

00:07:06.500 --> 00:07:07.900 line:80%
is indeed not Mu Zhengming,

00:07:08.570 --> 00:07:10.516 line:80%
so Mu Qingyan isn't
the skin-painted demon's son.

00:07:11.170 --> 00:07:12.010 line:80%
Why not

00:07:13.780 --> 00:07:14.970 line:80%
show mercy

00:07:14.970 --> 00:07:15.810 line:80%
where possible?

00:07:16.500 --> 00:07:17.340 line:80%
That won't do.

00:07:17.940 --> 00:07:19.380 line:80%
Pingshu can't die in vain.

00:07:20.850 --> 00:07:22.163 line:80%
As long as he bears the Mu name,

00:07:22.850 --> 00:07:24.780 line:80%
he must pay the price.

00:07:24.780 --> 00:07:25.650 line:80%
You want to kill him?

00:07:28.090 --> 00:07:29.023 line:80%
I think that is unwise.

00:07:29.730 --> 00:07:31.410 line:80%
He's the Young Master
of the demonic sect.

00:07:31.940 --> 00:07:33.170 line:80%
If he dies in Qingque Sect,

00:07:33.730 --> 00:07:35.500 line:80%
the demonic sect will never let it go.

00:07:36.020 --> 00:07:36.860 line:80%
When that happens,

00:07:37.460 --> 00:07:38.850 line:80%
war will reignite,

00:07:39.460 --> 00:07:40.953 line:80%
and Jianghu will lose its peace again.

00:07:42.140 --> 00:07:43.380 line:80%
I'm also worried about Zhao.

00:07:43.940 --> 00:07:45.380 line:80%
Did you see her last night?

00:07:46.090 --> 00:07:47.210 line:80%
I fear she has developed

00:07:48.290 --> 00:07:49.340 line:80%
feelings for that Mu boy.

00:08:03.090 --> 00:08:04.050 line:80%
Where is Mu Qingyan?

00:08:04.050 --> 00:08:04.890 line:80%
The Discipline Hall.

00:08:04.976 --> 00:08:06.006 line:80%
His life is not in danger.

00:08:06.050 --> 00:08:07.030 line:80%
I want to see him myself.

00:08:08.380 --> 00:08:09.220 line:80%
Milady!

00:08:09.730 --> 00:08:10.683 line:80%
Master has given orders.

00:08:10.940 --> 00:08:11.780 line:80%
Move aside.

00:08:11.780 --> 00:08:12.620 line:80%
Zhao.

00:08:14.500 --> 00:08:15.500 line:80%
Are you stopping me too?

00:08:15.850 --> 00:08:17.380 line:80%
This has already blown up.

00:08:17.380 --> 00:08:18.500 line:80%
The Six Sects are all here.

00:08:18.500 --> 00:08:19.580 line:80%
Everyone is watching you.

00:08:19.580 --> 00:08:21.090 line:80%
You must not wander off now.

00:08:21.090 --> 00:08:22.650 line:80%
Master asked us to stop you

00:08:22.650 --> 00:08:23.820 line:80%
to protect you.

00:08:28.700 --> 00:08:30.153 line:80%
Let Master and the others handle it.

00:08:31.410 --> 00:08:32.350 line:80%
What do you want to eat?

00:08:32.500 --> 00:08:33.340 line:80%
I'll bring it to you.

00:08:38.980 --> 00:08:40.050 line:80%
What?

00:08:40.050 --> 00:08:42.330 line:80%
Nie Zhe has reclaimed
Bliss Palace so soon?

00:08:42.330 --> 00:08:43.980 line:80%
Can you not be so agitated?

00:08:43.980 --> 00:08:44.900 line:80%
Come on.

00:08:44.900 --> 00:08:46.140 line:80%
I heard Mu Qingyan

00:08:46.140 --> 00:08:47.020 line:80%
refused all advice

00:08:47.020 --> 00:08:48.620 line:80%
and insisted on coming here,

00:08:48.620 --> 00:08:50.280 line:80%
even falling out with his subordinates.

00:08:50.740 --> 00:08:53.810 line:80%
His trusted aides
only defected to Nie Zhe

00:08:53.810 --> 00:08:55.570 line:80%
to save their own lives.

00:08:55.570 --> 00:08:57.290 line:80%
He brought this upon himself.

00:08:58.290 --> 00:08:59.290 line:80%
In that case,

00:08:59.860 --> 00:09:01.220 line:80%
there is no need for further trial.

00:09:01.220 --> 00:09:02.650 line:80%
Just slice him into pieces

00:09:03.290 --> 00:09:04.780 line:80%
to avenge Lord Wang.

00:09:04.780 --> 00:09:05.620 line:80%
No, no.

00:09:06.170 --> 00:09:07.010 line:80%
I don't think

00:09:07.319 --> 00:09:08.432 line:80%
killing him is appropriate.

00:09:08.530 --> 00:09:11.410 line:80%
Before, we feared sparking a war.

00:09:11.410 --> 00:09:12.900 line:80%
Now, he is no longer the Chief.

00:09:12.900 --> 00:09:14.100 line:80%
Why is it still not allowed?

00:09:15.020 --> 00:09:15.860 line:80%
Could it be

00:09:16.330 --> 00:09:19.530 line:80%
you have some ties with this fiend?

00:09:24.450 --> 00:09:25.290 line:80%
Li,

00:09:25.500 --> 00:09:27.140 line:80%
I have only met him a few times.

00:09:27.140 --> 00:09:29.330 line:80%
What ties could I possibly have?

00:09:29.330 --> 00:09:30.930 line:80%
If we kill Mu Qingyan,

00:09:30.930 --> 00:09:32.769 line:80%
wouldn't that play right
into Nie Zhe's hands?

00:09:33.930 --> 00:09:35.810 line:80%
Nie Zhe seized power only yesterday,

00:09:35.810 --> 00:09:38.100 line:80%
and the news has already reached here.

00:09:38.100 --> 00:09:40.690 line:80%
Clearly, he knows
we captured Mu Qingyan.

00:09:40.690 --> 00:09:42.020 line:80%
He wants to use us as a blade.

00:09:42.530 --> 00:09:45.450 line:80%
He hopes we dispose of Mu Qingyan asap

00:09:45.450 --> 00:09:47.050 line:80%
so his position will be secure.

00:09:47.650 --> 00:09:48.570 line:80%
Song is right.

00:09:49.170 --> 00:09:50.620 line:80%
Whether Lord Wang's death

00:09:50.620 --> 00:09:52.220 line:80%
has anything to do with Mu Qingyan

00:09:52.220 --> 00:09:53.400 line:80%
is still unclear.

00:09:53.620 --> 00:09:54.570 line:80%
Compared to Mu Qingyan,

00:09:54.570 --> 00:09:55.643 line:80%
Nie Zhe is more detestable.

00:09:55.900 --> 00:09:57.330 line:80%
We can't grant his wish.

00:09:57.330 --> 00:09:58.330 line:80%
Lady Ning...

00:09:58.330 --> 00:09:59.780 line:80%
Even without Lord Wang's matter,

00:10:00.050 --> 00:10:01.620 line:80%
the Mu clan caused Pingshu's death.

00:10:02.050 --> 00:10:03.650 line:80%
That is an undeniable fact.

00:10:04.020 --> 00:10:04.860 line:80%
No matter what,

00:10:05.170 --> 00:10:06.220 line:80%
we can't let him go.

00:10:07.050 --> 00:10:07.900 line:80%
Zhizhen is right.

00:10:08.810 --> 00:10:09.980 line:80%
When the Six Sects act,

00:10:10.620 --> 00:10:11.900 line:80%
we distinguish right from wrong.

00:10:12.380 --> 00:10:13.290 line:80%
If it's right,

00:10:13.290 --> 00:10:15.290 line:80%
we'll do it, however hard it may be.

00:10:15.570 --> 00:10:16.410 line:80%
If it's wrong,

00:10:17.380 --> 00:10:19.450 line:80%
we won't do it, whatever the benefit is.

00:10:19.980 --> 00:10:20.980 line:80%
That may be so,

00:10:21.530 --> 00:10:22.370 line:80%
but right now,

00:10:22.930 --> 00:10:24.450 line:80%
opinions are divided.

00:10:24.450 --> 00:10:26.100 line:80%
A decision must be made soon.

00:10:27.100 --> 00:10:27.940 line:80%
A blood debt

00:10:28.690 --> 00:10:29.710 line:80%
must be repaid with blood.

00:10:30.740 --> 00:10:31.580 line:80%
Zhou.

00:10:31.930 --> 00:10:32.860 line:80%
What do you mean?

00:10:33.380 --> 00:10:35.170 line:80%
Mu Qingyan didn't kill

00:10:35.170 --> 00:10:37.690 line:80%
a Six Sects member.

00:10:37.690 --> 00:10:38.810 line:80%
But the Mu clan's debt

00:10:39.620 --> 00:10:41.050 line:80%
must be paid by him.

00:10:41.450 --> 00:10:42.290 line:80%
Three days from now,

00:10:42.526 --> 00:10:43.795 line:80%
the Six Sects will hold a trial,

00:10:43.860 --> 00:10:45.479 line:80%
announce it before heaven and ancestors,

00:10:46.220 --> 00:10:47.810 line:80%
abolish his dantian and meridians,

00:10:47.810 --> 00:10:49.140 line:80%
strip him of all cultivation,

00:10:49.140 --> 00:10:50.290 line:80%
and imprison him for life.

00:10:50.290 --> 00:10:51.740 line:80%
He'll never see daylight again.

00:10:55.780 --> 00:10:56.833 line:80%
I think that's acceptable.

00:10:59.930 --> 00:11:00.770 line:80%
Very well.

00:11:01.050 --> 00:11:01.890 line:80%
It's settled.

00:11:08.900 --> 00:11:10.940 line:80%
(Discipline Hall)

00:11:39.020 --> 00:11:39.980 line:80%
Mu Qingyan,

00:11:40.380 --> 00:11:42.290 line:80%
you killed Lord Wang

00:11:42.980 --> 00:11:44.810 line:80%
and slandered Taichu Temple.

00:11:45.330 --> 00:11:46.170 line:80%
This revenge

00:11:47.220 --> 00:11:48.060 line:80%
I must take.

00:11:48.900 --> 00:11:49.740 line:80%
So,

00:11:50.740 --> 00:11:52.500 line:80%
they don't intend to kill me.

00:11:52.500 --> 00:11:54.140 line:80%
Even if they do not,

00:11:54.310 --> 00:11:55.600 line:80%
I won't let you live.

00:12:00.220 --> 00:12:01.930 line:80%
Master has decided Mr. Mu's punishment.

00:12:02.780 --> 00:12:03.780 line:80%
Before the execution,

00:12:04.290 --> 00:12:05.690 line:80%
no one may approach him.

00:12:06.530 --> 00:12:07.780 line:80%
I don't want his life.

00:12:09.020 --> 00:12:10.220 line:80%
I'll sever one arm and one leg

00:12:10.220 --> 00:12:11.570 line:80%
and spare his life, okay?

00:12:11.570 --> 00:12:12.620 line:80%
This is grave.

00:12:12.620 --> 00:12:14.900 line:80%
If you truly wish to maim him,

00:12:14.900 --> 00:12:16.450 line:80%
discuss with Master first.

00:12:16.980 --> 00:12:19.290 line:80%
You're bullying us when we're declining.

00:12:19.290 --> 00:12:21.020 line:80%
Then we will fight to the death.

00:12:21.020 --> 00:12:22.980 line:80%
To preserve Taichu Temple's reputation,

00:12:22.980 --> 00:12:25.650 line:80%
Master ordered us to remain silent
about Lord Wang's matter.

00:12:25.650 --> 00:12:27.290 line:80%
But if you persist,

00:12:27.290 --> 00:12:29.220 line:80%
the news may leak.

00:12:29.220 --> 00:12:31.620 line:80%
Surely, you don't want

00:12:31.620 --> 00:12:32.980 line:80%
Lord Wang to die bearing slander.

00:12:33.570 --> 00:12:36.290 line:80%
I know Lord Wang was gentle
and benevolent,

00:12:36.290 --> 00:12:37.620 line:80%
like a father to you.

00:12:37.620 --> 00:12:38.900 line:80%
Everyone said he was a good man.

00:12:39.620 --> 00:12:41.140 line:80%
But good men can make mistakes.

00:12:42.500 --> 00:12:44.100 line:80%
Good men can stray.

00:12:46.780 --> 00:12:47.620 line:80%
Li Min,

00:12:48.410 --> 00:12:49.380 line:80%
please return.

00:12:59.330 --> 00:13:00.170 line:80%
Song,

00:13:01.020 --> 00:13:01.980 line:80%
you won't leave?

00:13:08.620 --> 00:13:09.460 line:80%
Don't worry.

00:13:09.810 --> 00:13:10.650 line:80%
Before the execution,

00:13:11.760 --> 00:13:13.120 line:80%
I won't let you be humiliated.

00:13:14.500 --> 00:13:15.480 line:80%
Where is Zhao?

00:13:16.140 --> 00:13:17.770 line:80%
She is being watched by Uncle Li.

00:13:19.050 --> 00:13:19.890 line:80%
Mr. Mu,

00:13:21.500 --> 00:13:22.790 line:80%
why did you come?

00:13:23.690 --> 00:13:24.980 line:80%
I promised her

00:13:26.380 --> 00:13:27.740 line:80%
I'd give her an explanation.

00:13:28.290 --> 00:13:29.410 line:80%
There are many ways

00:13:29.410 --> 00:13:30.396 line:80%
to offer an explanation.

00:13:31.530 --> 00:13:33.330 line:80%
Why insist on coming here?

00:13:35.530 --> 00:13:36.370 line:80%
Only this way

00:13:38.650 --> 00:13:39.740 line:80%
would Zhao believe me.

00:13:40.380 --> 00:13:41.726 line:80%
You don't want her to believe you.

00:13:42.650 --> 00:13:43.810 line:80%
You want to force her.

00:13:43.810 --> 00:13:45.020 line:80%
You know well

00:13:45.860 --> 00:13:46.740 line:80%
that Pingshu's death

00:13:46.740 --> 00:13:48.780 line:80%
is tied to the Mu clan.

00:13:49.410 --> 00:13:50.930 line:80%
Let alone Zhao,

00:13:50.930 --> 00:13:53.170 line:80%
even Master and the others
won't forgive you.

00:13:53.170 --> 00:13:54.780 line:80%
If you had not come,

00:13:54.780 --> 00:13:55.780 line:80%
even with an explanation,

00:13:55.780 --> 00:13:58.050 line:80%
she'd never be with you again.

00:13:58.050 --> 00:13:59.930 line:80%
So, you wagered your life,

00:13:59.930 --> 00:14:01.740 line:80%
betting she wouldn't watch you die

00:14:03.450 --> 00:14:04.380 line:80%
and she'd choose

00:14:04.380 --> 00:14:06.100 line:80%
between her sect and you.

00:14:08.690 --> 00:14:09.570 line:80%
Song, how well

00:14:10.780 --> 00:14:11.620 line:80%
you know me.

00:14:12.500 --> 00:14:13.340 line:80%
Song,

00:14:14.050 --> 00:14:15.380 line:80%
do you think I'll win this bet?

00:14:19.690 --> 00:14:20.530 line:80%
Madman.

00:14:24.380 --> 00:14:25.980 line:80%
To abolish all his meridians

00:14:25.980 --> 00:14:26.820 line:80%
and imprison him?

00:14:51.450 --> 00:14:52.290 line:80%
Zhao,

00:14:52.500 --> 00:14:53.930 line:80%
you must not harbor foolish thoughts.

00:14:54.780 --> 00:14:56.220 line:80%
The Six Sects are on lockdown.

00:14:56.220 --> 00:14:57.530 line:80%
The demonic sect is in chaos.

00:14:57.530 --> 00:14:58.803 line:80%
No one will help you rescue him.

00:14:59.330 --> 00:15:01.682 line:80%
Given the feud between the Six Sects
and the demonic sect,

00:15:01.693 --> 00:15:03.483 line:80%
your master agreeing to spare his life

00:15:03.780 --> 00:15:05.050 line:80%
is already magnanimous.

00:15:08.570 --> 00:15:09.410 line:80%
At least,

00:15:10.100 --> 00:15:10.940 line:80%
he will live.

00:15:11.410 --> 00:15:13.616 line:80%
He was imprisoned by Nie Zhe
for five years as a child.

00:15:14.570 --> 00:15:15.596 line:80%
If he is locked up again,

00:15:16.380 --> 00:15:17.860 line:80%
he might as well die.

00:15:27.690 --> 00:15:28.530 line:80%
Zhao,

00:15:28.690 --> 00:15:30.020 line:80%
your mother and I discussed this.

00:15:31.020 --> 00:15:31.860 line:80%
If

00:15:32.330 --> 00:15:33.500 line:80%
you truly can't bear it,

00:15:33.690 --> 00:15:34.620 line:80%
after the execution,

00:15:34.860 --> 00:15:35.970 line:80%
I'll bring him back

00:15:36.290 --> 00:15:37.170 line:80%
to Luoying Valley.

00:15:38.140 --> 00:15:38.980 line:80%
What do you think?

00:15:51.810 --> 00:15:52.650 line:80%
Yes, yes.

00:15:53.690 --> 00:15:55.380 line:80%
Luoying Valley is best for recovery.

00:15:55.380 --> 00:15:57.020 line:80%
You know what I'm capable of.

00:15:57.020 --> 00:15:58.900 line:80%
Though his cultivation
will be abolished,

00:15:58.900 --> 00:15:59.860 line:80%
I guarantee

00:15:59.860 --> 00:16:01.500 line:80%
he'll live peacefully and healthily

00:16:01.500 --> 00:16:02.493 line:80%
for the rest of his life.

00:16:08.140 --> 00:16:09.290 line:80%
As long as he is safe.

00:16:24.290 --> 00:16:25.130 line:80%
Xingjia.

00:16:26.620 --> 00:16:27.740 line:80%
Bringing food to Zhao again?

00:16:28.170 --> 00:16:29.040 line:80%
Yes.

00:16:29.050 --> 00:16:31.020 line:80%
She's returned it untouched these days.

00:16:31.020 --> 00:16:32.140 line:80%
It feels pointless.

00:16:32.570 --> 00:16:33.410 line:80%
Mr. Mu

00:16:33.810 --> 00:16:34.970 line:80%
doesn't look like a bad man,

00:16:36.140 --> 00:16:38.740 line:80%
but he is still the Chief
of the demonic sect.

00:16:39.050 --> 00:16:40.650 line:80%
Zhao is not one who believes

00:16:40.650 --> 00:16:42.860 line:80%
that good and evil must never coexist.

00:16:42.860 --> 00:16:44.570 line:80%
What truly pains her

00:16:44.570 --> 00:16:45.810 line:80%
is that her most respected aunt

00:16:45.810 --> 00:16:46.900 line:80%
was harmed by the Mu clan.

00:16:48.380 --> 00:16:49.220 line:80%
You don't get it.

00:16:49.500 --> 00:16:51.740 line:80%
This time, Mr. Mu was captured
while seeking her.

00:16:52.290 --> 00:16:53.740 line:80%
Zhao

00:16:53.740 --> 00:16:55.380 line:80%
must be shocked,

00:16:55.740 --> 00:16:56.620 line:80%
guilty,

00:16:57.140 --> 00:16:58.020 line:80%
heartbroken,

00:16:58.530 --> 00:16:59.370 line:80%
and lost.

00:17:00.290 --> 00:17:01.130 line:80%
But tomorrow

00:17:02.690 --> 00:17:03.530 line:80%
is the execution.

00:17:03.890 --> 00:17:05.660 line:80%
I only hope she can eat something

00:17:06.530 --> 00:17:07.370 line:80%
and get through this.

00:17:22.570 --> 00:17:23.410 line:80%
Zhao,

00:17:23.850 --> 00:17:25.020 line:80%
at least eat a little.

00:17:25.460 --> 00:17:26.890 line:80%
Mr. Mu has not been executed yet.

00:17:27.090 --> 00:17:27.930 line:80%
You can't collapse

00:17:29.330 --> 00:17:30.610 line:80%
before he does.

00:17:31.700 --> 00:17:32.540 line:80%
Zhao,

00:17:35.290 --> 00:17:36.610 line:80%
you are eating?

00:17:36.610 --> 00:17:37.530 line:80%
Feicui brought it.

00:17:37.530 --> 00:17:39.050 line:80%
Xingjia, did you bring anything good?

00:17:42.810 --> 00:17:43.650 line:80%
Here.

00:17:45.130 --> 00:17:46.290 line:80%
Yes.

00:17:46.290 --> 00:17:47.500 line:80%
Crispy pigeon,

00:17:48.130 --> 00:17:49.050 line:80%
assorted duck,

00:17:49.050 --> 00:17:50.020 line:80%
spring rolls,

00:17:50.020 --> 00:17:51.059 line:80%
and salted egg roast pork.

00:17:51.460 --> 00:17:52.700 line:80%
I watched the chef make them.

00:17:56.420 --> 00:17:57.260 line:80%
How is it?

00:17:57.460 --> 00:17:58.460 line:80%
The duck soup is good.

00:18:00.290 --> 00:18:01.500 line:80%
But the pigeon

00:18:01.500 --> 00:18:02.340 line:80%
lacks a bit of heat.

00:18:03.530 --> 00:18:04.700 line:80%
That is my Zhao.

00:18:05.020 --> 00:18:06.420 line:80%
Rushing to deliver food

00:18:06.420 --> 00:18:07.530 line:80%
does affect the timing.

00:18:07.530 --> 00:18:08.370 line:80%
Eat more duck.

00:18:10.330 --> 00:18:11.170 line:80%
Zhao,

00:18:11.627 --> 00:18:12.787 line:80%
it's good you've accepted it.

00:18:13.020 --> 00:18:13.860 line:80%
Actually,

00:18:14.290 --> 00:18:15.460 line:80%
we also hate

00:18:15.460 --> 00:18:16.780 line:80%
to see Mr. Mu punished.

00:18:17.220 --> 00:18:18.660 line:80%
But all Six Sects are present.

00:18:19.130 --> 00:18:21.130 line:80%
He's indeed the Chief
of the demonic sect.

00:18:21.610 --> 00:18:22.610 line:80%
Lord Wang's death

00:18:23.180 --> 00:18:24.530 line:80%
requires an explanation.

00:18:25.130 --> 00:18:26.530 line:80%
There is no room to maneuver.

00:18:27.290 --> 00:18:28.370 line:80%
Don't worry, Xingjia.

00:18:28.850 --> 00:18:29.963 line:80%
I've come to terms with it.

00:18:31.050 --> 00:18:32.290 line:80%
At worst, it's death.

00:18:34.020 --> 00:18:34.860 line:80%
What?

00:18:37.500 --> 00:18:38.810 line:80%
In Jianghu,

00:18:38.810 --> 00:18:39.650 line:80%
debts are clear.

00:18:40.050 --> 00:18:41.570 line:80%
Mu Qingyan was captured because of me.

00:18:41.940 --> 00:18:42.780 line:80%
He is proud.

00:18:43.330 --> 00:18:44.420 line:80%
If he becomes invalid,

00:18:44.700 --> 00:18:45.890 line:80%
he won't live on.

00:18:46.740 --> 00:18:48.570 line:80%
I can't let him walk that path alone.

00:18:48.570 --> 00:18:49.420 line:80%
I don't have

00:18:49.430 --> 00:18:50.370 line:80%
many meals left.

00:18:50.980 --> 00:18:52.473 line:80%
Xingjia, whatever good food you have,

00:18:52.610 --> 00:18:53.450 line:80%
bring it all.

00:18:53.890 --> 00:18:55.290 line:80%
Zhao, what are you doing?

00:18:55.610 --> 00:18:57.530 line:80%
Of course, I'll die

00:18:58.050 --> 00:18:59.290 line:80%
with him.

00:19:01.370 --> 00:19:02.290 line:80%
Zhao,

00:19:02.290 --> 00:19:03.130 line:80%
don't scare me.

00:19:04.850 --> 00:19:06.570 line:80%
No need to mourn so soon.

00:19:07.290 --> 00:19:08.370 line:80%
Wait until I'm buried

00:19:08.370 --> 00:19:10.570 line:80%
with Mu Qingyan.

00:19:11.370 --> 00:19:12.890 line:80%
Then you can pay respects.

00:19:13.810 --> 00:19:14.810 line:80%
Zhao,

00:19:14.810 --> 00:19:16.330 line:80%
please reconsider.

00:19:16.330 --> 00:19:17.290 line:80%
Please.

00:19:25.980 --> 00:19:26.820 line:80%
Hold it steady.

00:19:27.050 --> 00:19:28.020 line:80%
How clumsy.

00:19:29.090 --> 00:19:29.930 line:80%
Fengchi.

00:19:30.130 --> 00:19:30.970 line:80%
Xingjia.

00:19:32.426 --> 00:19:33.890 line:80%
We need to change Mr. Mu's medicine.

00:19:33.890 --> 00:19:34.730 line:80%
Stop.

00:19:38.980 --> 00:19:39.820 line:80%
What is it?

00:19:40.180 --> 00:19:41.020 line:80%
Does that

00:19:41.780 --> 00:19:42.780 line:80%
require two people?

00:19:44.020 --> 00:19:45.290 line:80%
Of course.

00:19:45.290 --> 00:19:46.370 line:80%
Fengchi,

00:19:46.370 --> 00:19:47.220 line:80%
Mr. Mu

00:19:47.220 --> 00:19:48.530 line:80%
is covered in wounds.

00:19:48.530 --> 00:19:50.220 line:80%
It'd be exhausting alone.

00:19:50.220 --> 00:19:51.130 line:80%
Go by yourself.

00:19:51.850 --> 00:19:52.940 line:80%
Young man,

00:19:53.780 --> 00:19:54.850 line:80%
come with me.

00:19:58.290 --> 00:19:59.220 line:80%
Fengchi,

00:19:59.220 --> 00:20:00.753 line:80%
didn't you say you'd practice with me?

00:20:00.980 --> 00:20:01.820 line:80%
Let's go.

00:20:02.780 --> 00:20:03.620 line:80%
Lingbo.

00:20:03.850 --> 00:20:05.020 line:80%
Let's go.

00:20:05.020 --> 00:20:05.910 line:80%
I've been waiting.

00:20:05.920 --> 00:20:06.790 line:80%
Let's go.

00:20:07.950 --> 00:20:08.810 line:80%
Come on.

00:20:08.810 --> 00:20:10.340 line:80%
Clumsy fool. Open the door.

00:20:12.890 --> 00:20:13.740 line:80%
Hurry.

00:20:14.940 --> 00:20:15.780 line:80%
Lingbo,

00:20:16.460 --> 00:20:17.806 line:80%
why didn't you let me expose her?

00:20:18.090 --> 00:20:19.610 line:80%
Qingque Sect is under lockdown.

00:20:20.290 --> 00:20:22.306 line:80%
Mu Qingyan can't escape anyway.

00:20:22.317 --> 00:20:23.449 line:80%
If Cai Zhao wants to see him,

00:20:23.460 --> 00:20:24.130 line:80%
let her.

00:20:24.420 --> 00:20:25.260 line:80%
You...

00:20:25.570 --> 00:20:27.130 line:80%
Don't you hate Cai Zhao?

00:20:27.130 --> 00:20:28.180 line:80%
Yeah.

00:20:29.980 --> 00:20:31.430 line:80%
But Mu Qingyan risked his life

00:20:32.370 --> 00:20:34.130 line:80%
to see her,

00:20:34.130 --> 00:20:35.700 line:80%
facing my father and the others

00:20:35.700 --> 00:20:38.220 line:80%
without retreat.

00:20:38.220 --> 00:20:39.460 line:80%
That shows some sincerity.

00:20:40.050 --> 00:20:41.490 line:80%
I'm willing to grant them this once.

00:20:44.560 --> 00:20:45.420 line:80%
But

00:20:45.420 --> 00:20:46.793 line:80%
even if she goes in, it's useless.

00:20:50.180 --> 00:20:51.050 line:80%
Where is he?

00:20:53.290 --> 00:20:54.290 line:80%
You can't see him.

00:20:57.940 --> 00:20:58.810 line:80%
You

00:20:59.420 --> 00:21:00.290 line:80%
killed him?

00:21:03.050 --> 00:21:03.890 line:80%
Uncle Li,

00:21:04.180 --> 00:21:05.290 line:80%
if Mr. Mu dies,

00:21:05.290 --> 00:21:06.660 line:80%
Zhao won't live either.

00:21:07.050 --> 00:21:08.660 line:80%
If she seeks death over this,

00:21:09.026 --> 00:21:11.186 line:80%
she doesn't deserve to be
a disciple of the Six Sects.

00:21:11.700 --> 00:21:12.700 line:80%
Zhao,

00:21:12.700 --> 00:21:13.850 line:80%
Mu Qingyan is not dead.

00:21:13.850 --> 00:21:15.780 line:80%
To prevent a rescue by the demonic sect,

00:21:15.780 --> 00:21:16.940 line:80%
he's been moved elsewhere.

00:21:18.420 --> 00:21:19.850 line:80%
Don't act rashly.

00:21:21.980 --> 00:21:22.850 line:80%
Uncle Li,

00:21:23.460 --> 00:21:24.460 line:80%
Uncle Zhou,

00:21:28.500 --> 00:21:30.020 line:80%
I only want to see him once.

00:21:30.020 --> 00:21:30.860 line:80%
With you watching,

00:21:30.870 --> 00:21:31.860 line:80%
I can't rescue him.

00:21:32.050 --> 00:21:33.483 line:80%
I only wish to see him one last time

00:21:33.494 --> 00:21:34.460 line:80%
before the execution.

00:21:34.460 --> 00:21:35.500 line:80%
Yes, Uncle Li.

00:21:35.500 --> 00:21:37.220 line:80%
Zhao is one of us.

00:21:37.220 --> 00:21:38.420 line:80%
Let them meet once.

00:21:38.420 --> 00:21:39.700 line:80%
The execution is tomorrow.

00:21:39.700 --> 00:21:41.020 line:80%
The outcome is already decided.

00:21:41.020 --> 00:21:42.570 line:80%
Grant her this wish.

00:21:42.570 --> 00:21:43.460 line:80%
Nonsense.

00:21:44.330 --> 00:21:45.170 line:80%
Zhao,

00:21:45.740 --> 00:21:47.290 line:80%
I know you like Mu Qingyan,

00:21:47.700 --> 00:21:49.330 line:80%
but he is not worth it.

00:21:49.660 --> 00:21:50.610 line:80%
From now on,

00:21:50.610 --> 00:21:51.500 line:80%
forget him.

00:21:54.050 --> 00:21:55.500 line:80%
Why is he not worth liking?

00:21:57.330 --> 00:21:58.660 line:80%
Because his surname is Mu.

00:22:03.090 --> 00:22:04.500 line:80%
What do the Mu clan's past sins

00:22:04.810 --> 00:22:05.740 line:80%
have to do with him?

00:22:06.220 --> 00:22:07.130 line:80%
He's never harmed me,

00:22:08.020 --> 00:22:09.980 line:80%
nor committed injustice
against the Six Sects.

00:22:09.980 --> 00:22:11.460 line:80%
The only killing he ever did

00:22:11.890 --> 00:22:13.700 line:80%
was when Nie Zhe drove him to the brink,

00:22:13.700 --> 00:22:15.290 line:80%
just to survive.

00:22:15.290 --> 00:22:16.930 line:80%
His hands are far cleaner
than Yin Dai's.

00:22:17.570 --> 00:22:18.700 line:80%
He's never wronged me.

00:22:20.780 --> 00:22:22.020 line:80%
His devotion to me

00:22:22.020 --> 00:22:23.020 line:80%
surpasses mine to him.

00:22:23.890 --> 00:22:24.980 line:80%
Why can I not like him?

00:22:25.330 --> 00:22:26.370 line:80%
Why must I forget him?

00:22:26.370 --> 00:22:27.210 line:80%
Silence.

00:22:32.700 --> 00:22:34.180 line:80%
Zhao truly said that?

00:22:34.500 --> 00:22:37.460 line:80%
Even if Luoying Valley
has always acted freely,

00:22:38.120 --> 00:22:39.560 line:80%
you can't blur right and wrong.

00:22:40.420 --> 00:22:41.260 line:80%
Ning,

00:22:41.460 --> 00:22:43.290 line:80%
you must discipline your daughter.

00:22:43.290 --> 00:22:44.130 line:80%
Why?

00:22:44.850 --> 00:22:46.460 line:80%
I think my girl is right.

00:22:46.740 --> 00:22:47.890 line:80%
Right?

00:22:47.890 --> 00:22:48.956 line:80%
Confusing black and white,

00:22:50.020 --> 00:22:51.020 line:80%
and that is not wrong?

00:22:52.050 --> 00:22:54.220 line:80%
Mu Qingyan came for Zhao.

00:22:54.220 --> 00:22:55.660 line:80%
And he was captured.

00:22:55.660 --> 00:22:57.130 line:80%
If Zhao acts

00:22:57.130 --> 00:22:58.090 line:80%
as if nothing happened,

00:22:58.090 --> 00:22:59.220 line:80%
that'd be despicable

00:22:59.220 --> 00:23:00.500 line:80%
and shameless,

00:23:01.180 --> 00:23:02.570 line:80%
against martial honor.

00:23:03.130 --> 00:23:04.220 line:80%
Luoying Valley

00:23:04.220 --> 00:23:06.780 line:80%
doesn't raise hypocrites
who only protect themselves.

00:23:07.370 --> 00:23:08.210 line:80%
Ning,

00:23:08.460 --> 00:23:09.980 line:80%
Mu Qingyan is not like the bandits

00:23:09.980 --> 00:23:11.825 line:80%
you hide in Luoying Valley.

00:23:11.836 --> 00:23:13.220 line:80%
He's the Chief of the demonic sect.

00:23:13.220 --> 00:23:14.180 line:80%
So what?

00:23:14.700 --> 00:23:16.130 line:80%
Does that make him evil?

00:23:17.130 --> 00:23:18.460 line:80%
The Six Sects are so righteous?

00:23:18.780 --> 00:23:19.700 line:80%
Think about it.

00:23:20.370 --> 00:23:22.500 line:80%
Wang Yuanjing, Qiu Yuanfeng,

00:23:22.500 --> 00:23:23.780 line:80%
and Yin Dai.

00:23:23.780 --> 00:23:25.420 line:80%
What good deeds have they done?

00:23:25.420 --> 00:23:26.520 line:80%
Worse than the demonic sect.

00:23:27.850 --> 00:23:28.940 line:80%
Let me tell you.

00:23:28.940 --> 00:23:30.570 line:80%
If not for Qi,

00:23:30.570 --> 00:23:31.740 line:80%
I wouldn't have let Zhao

00:23:31.740 --> 00:23:32.740 line:80%
stay in Qingque Sect.

00:23:33.780 --> 00:23:35.460 line:80%
This Double Lotus Palace

00:23:35.460 --> 00:23:37.460 line:80%
was bought with Zigui's life,

00:23:37.460 --> 00:23:40.220 line:80%
but I never even saw Zigui
one last time.

00:23:40.220 --> 00:23:42.330 line:80%
Just let Zhao see Mu Qingyan.

00:23:42.330 --> 00:23:43.330 line:80%
Is that not allowed?

00:23:43.330 --> 00:23:44.460 line:80%
But the Lord has ordered...

00:23:44.460 --> 00:23:45.406 line:80%
To hell with his order.

00:23:47.020 --> 00:23:48.050 line:80%
If you keep talking,

00:23:48.050 --> 00:23:49.330 line:80%
I'll expose

00:23:49.330 --> 00:23:50.660 line:80%
everything Yin Dai did.

00:23:50.660 --> 00:23:51.780 line:80%
Let everyone judge.

00:23:52.660 --> 00:23:54.530 line:80%
And Lord Wang as well.

00:23:55.050 --> 00:23:56.180 line:80%
We might as well split apart.

00:23:56.610 --> 00:23:58.570 line:80%
I say the Six Sects should disband.

00:24:12.020 --> 00:24:12.860 line:80%
Get out.

00:24:25.380 --> 00:24:26.780 line:80%
(Library)

00:24:27.940 --> 00:24:28.850 line:80%
Zhao,

00:24:30.220 --> 00:24:31.420 line:80%
why have you grown so thin?

00:24:32.880 --> 00:24:34.940 line:80%
Thank you, Yuzhi, for looking after him

00:24:35.370 --> 00:24:36.610 line:80%
and sparing him humiliation.

00:24:37.090 --> 00:24:38.180 line:80%
May I go in

00:24:38.180 --> 00:24:39.646 line:80%
and speak to him alone for a moment?

00:24:42.610 --> 00:24:43.450 line:80%
Yes.

00:25:13.530 --> 00:25:14.570 line:80%
Mu Qingyan.

00:25:18.530 --> 00:25:19.370 line:80%
Zhao.

00:25:20.740 --> 00:25:21.610 line:80%
Does it hurt?

00:25:38.460 --> 00:25:39.420 line:80%
Seeing you

00:25:41.130 --> 00:25:41.970 line:80%
is good enough.

00:25:44.810 --> 00:25:45.650 line:80%
Zhao,

00:25:47.370 --> 00:25:48.610 line:80%
the one who killed your aunt

00:25:49.530 --> 00:25:50.420 line:80%
wasn't my father.

00:25:51.610 --> 00:25:52.890 line:80%
- It's...
- I know.

00:25:53.420 --> 00:25:54.940 line:80%
I know it all now.

00:25:57.370 --> 00:25:59.370 line:80%
In fact, I never doubted you.

00:26:00.090 --> 00:26:01.530 line:80%
You only needed to send word,

00:26:02.050 --> 00:26:03.180 line:80%
as you did before.

00:26:03.940 --> 00:26:05.740 line:80%
Why insist on coming here?

00:26:05.740 --> 00:26:07.290 line:80%
I feared you'd never see me again.

00:26:11.940 --> 00:26:13.370 line:80%
- Tomorrow...
- I know.

00:26:14.180 --> 00:26:15.460 line:80%
Song Yuzhi told me.

00:26:18.090 --> 00:26:19.263 line:80%
After the execution tomorrow,

00:26:20.020 --> 00:26:21.980 line:80%
they will imprison you in the dungeon.

00:26:29.130 --> 00:26:30.330 line:80%
Take

00:26:30.980 --> 00:26:31.820 line:80%
this luminous pearl.

00:26:36.330 --> 00:26:37.343 line:80%
You're afraid of the dark.

00:26:37.850 --> 00:26:38.940 line:80%
With it,

00:26:39.370 --> 00:26:41.090 line:80%
you can at least sleep peacefully.

00:26:41.890 --> 00:26:43.220 line:80%
How do you know I fear the dark?

00:26:49.780 --> 00:26:50.890 line:80%
Are you afraid of the dark?

00:26:51.850 --> 00:26:53.260 line:80%
- Don't be.
- I'm not afraid.

00:26:53.850 --> 00:26:55.370 line:80%
You've always feared the dark,

00:26:56.290 --> 00:26:57.610 line:80%
but you never admit it.

00:27:03.890 --> 00:27:05.570 line:80%
From now on, alone in the dungeon,

00:27:06.130 --> 00:27:07.530 line:80%
don't push yourself too hard.

00:27:17.610 --> 00:27:19.290 line:80%
So, you say all this

00:27:19.660 --> 00:27:20.740 line:80%
and give me a pearl

00:27:22.020 --> 00:27:23.610 line:80%
just to ease your conscience.

00:27:28.020 --> 00:27:29.810 line:80%
Should I congratulate you

00:27:31.570 --> 00:27:33.890 line:80%
for finally ridding yourself of me?

00:27:36.940 --> 00:27:37.780 line:80%
What else?

00:27:40.780 --> 00:27:42.290 line:80%
What do you expect me to do?

00:27:42.850 --> 00:27:44.243 line:80%
Storm the execution ground for you?

00:27:44.780 --> 00:27:46.700 line:80%
Abandon my master and parents

00:27:47.570 --> 00:27:48.700 line:80%
and elope with you?

00:27:49.430 --> 00:27:51.770 line:80%
♪Seasons turn♪

00:27:53.210 --> 00:27:56.780 line:80%
♪Sun and moon fly like the shuttle♪

00:27:58.740 --> 00:28:02.510 line:80%
♪Yet why linger on what plagues us most♪

00:28:03.810 --> 00:28:05.330 line:80%
Have you considered me?

00:28:05.810 --> 00:28:06.810 line:80%
As I said,

00:28:08.090 --> 00:28:10.460 line:80%
I'd never forsake my family

00:28:10.460 --> 00:28:12.130 line:80%
and friends for anyone.

00:28:12.740 --> 00:28:14.890 line:80%
When you recklessly came here,

00:28:15.420 --> 00:28:16.660 line:80%
did you think of me at all?

00:28:17.290 --> 00:28:19.420 line:80%
I only want a peaceful life.

00:28:20.130 --> 00:28:21.330 line:80%
Why must you push me

00:28:21.330 --> 00:28:22.500 line:80%
again and again?

00:28:26.420 --> 00:28:27.740 line:80%
I push you?

00:28:27.740 --> 00:28:30.320 line:80%
♪In the blink of an eye♪

00:28:30.910 --> 00:28:35.630 line:80%
♪Unaware of when it all turns
to nothing♪

00:28:36.810 --> 00:28:38.420 line:80%
From the first time you provoked me,

00:28:39.090 --> 00:28:40.940 line:80%
did you think of the consequences?

00:28:40.940 --> 00:28:42.220 line:80%
When did I ever provoke you?

00:28:42.220 --> 00:28:43.980 line:80%
From the first time you stood before me,

00:28:49.906 --> 00:28:52.006 line:80%
the first time you appeared
in the Hanhai Mountains,

00:28:54.290 --> 00:28:55.740 line:80%
you had already provoked me.

00:28:57.180 --> 00:28:59.560 line:80%
♪Despite grievous sins♪

00:29:00.500 --> 00:29:05.430 line:80%
♪I only wish to stay with you♪

00:29:06.050 --> 00:29:09.860 line:80%
♪By the rugged emerald peaks♪

00:29:13.130 --> 00:29:14.290 line:80%
Cai Zhao, listen to me.

00:29:14.780 --> 00:29:16.500 line:80%
We can never be separated.

00:29:17.460 --> 00:29:19.290 line:80%
So what if my meridians are severed?

00:29:21.330 --> 00:29:23.220 line:80%
Even if I'm reduced to ashes,

00:29:24.530 --> 00:29:25.460 line:80%
I will...

00:29:27.330 --> 00:29:28.980 line:80%
I'll return to find you.

00:29:29.870 --> 00:29:32.430 line:80%
♪With a lone courage, I risk my life♪

00:29:33.200 --> 00:29:38.690 line:80%
♪Wishing to share
the dusk snow with you♪

00:29:41.660 --> 00:29:42.500 line:80%
You are mad.

00:29:43.130 --> 00:29:44.090 line:80%
Completely mad.

00:29:46.020 --> 00:29:46.860 line:80%
Mu Qingyan,

00:29:49.700 --> 00:29:50.700 line:80%
we sever all ties.

00:29:50.970 --> 00:29:56.110 line:80%
♪Unaware of when it all turns
to nothing♪

00:29:56.870 --> 00:30:01.670 line:80%
♪When our gazes meet, our hearts soften♪

00:30:01.670 --> 00:30:06.400 line:80%
♪Like clouds over a vast blue sky♪

00:30:08.530 --> 00:30:13.830 line:80%
♪Scheming for the world
with reckless valor♪

00:30:14.530 --> 00:30:20.380 line:80%
♪Throwing myself into love
despite grievous sins♪

00:30:20.600 --> 00:30:25.580 line:80%
♪I only wish to stay with you♪

00:30:25.990 --> 00:30:30.200 line:80%
♪By the rugged emerald peaks♪

00:30:30.200 --> 00:30:35.780 line:80%
♪Throwing myself into love
despite grievous sins♪

00:30:36.120 --> 00:30:40.970 line:80%
♪I only wish to stay with you♪

00:30:41.590 --> 00:30:46.650 line:80%
♪By the rugged emerald peaks♪

00:30:47.930 --> 00:30:50.450 line:80%
♪You understand love and loyalty♪

00:30:51.400 --> 00:31:00.240 line:80%
♪Yet have nowhere to seek them♪

00:31:09.890 --> 00:31:10.730 line:80%
Yuzhi,

00:31:10.940 --> 00:31:11.780 line:80%
why are you here?

00:31:12.380 --> 00:31:13.420 line:80%
I've been looking for you.

00:31:16.130 --> 00:31:16.970 line:80%
What's wrong?

00:31:21.890 --> 00:31:23.190 line:80%
Since childhood,

00:31:23.290 --> 00:31:24.490 line:80%
I've never seen you like this.

00:31:25.010 --> 00:31:27.610 line:80%
Are you worried that Zhao will act?

00:31:29.480 --> 00:31:31.030 line:80%
Mu Qingyan once saved Zhao.

00:31:31.370 --> 00:31:33.420 line:80%
She'll never watch him be crippled.

00:31:33.420 --> 00:31:35.570 line:80%
Lord Wang's death
has nothing to do with him.

00:31:35.570 --> 00:31:36.536 line:80%
He doesn't deserve this.

00:31:36.780 --> 00:31:37.890 line:80%
If I plead for mercy,

00:31:38.220 --> 00:31:39.980 line:80%
will Master retract his order?

00:31:39.980 --> 00:31:42.890 line:80%
You are already speaking for Mu Qingyan.

00:31:42.890 --> 00:31:44.050 line:80%
If Zhao asks you

00:31:44.050 --> 00:31:45.980 line:80%
to help rescue him later,

00:31:45.980 --> 00:31:47.020 line:80%
will you agree?

00:31:49.020 --> 00:31:51.810 line:80%
Zhao cares about Master
and Luoying Valley's reputation.

00:31:51.810 --> 00:31:52.780 line:80%
She may plead,

00:31:52.963 --> 00:31:54.130 line:80%
but she won't act recklessly.

00:31:54.130 --> 00:31:55.460 line:80%
You

00:31:55.460 --> 00:31:57.660 line:80%
have been held back by your mother.

00:31:57.660 --> 00:32:00.020 line:80%
You always calculate before acting.

00:32:00.610 --> 00:32:01.530 line:80%
I was young once too.

00:32:02.330 --> 00:32:03.890 line:80%
How many youths

00:32:03.890 --> 00:32:05.810 line:80%
weigh every gain and loss before moving?

00:32:10.090 --> 00:32:11.180 line:80%
What do you mean?

00:32:12.740 --> 00:32:13.810 line:80%
Mark my words.

00:32:14.010 --> 00:32:15.890 line:80%
Without a great upheaval,

00:32:15.890 --> 00:32:17.500 line:80%
Zhao won't easily

00:32:17.500 --> 00:32:19.050 line:80%
give up on that Mu boy.

00:32:19.810 --> 00:32:22.370 line:80%
Whether she takes after her aunt

00:32:22.370 --> 00:32:23.370 line:80%
or Ning Xiaofeng,

00:32:24.220 --> 00:32:25.810 line:80%
she won't accept fate so readily.

00:32:26.530 --> 00:32:27.980 line:80%
The one she loves is to be crippled,

00:32:28.740 --> 00:32:30.660 line:80%
yet she neither fiercely resists

00:32:30.660 --> 00:32:32.700 line:80%
nor curses us and weeps.

00:32:34.180 --> 00:32:35.020 line:80%
It's too strange.

00:32:35.660 --> 00:32:36.500 line:80%
Son,

00:32:37.660 --> 00:32:39.280 line:80%
you must listen to me this time.

00:32:39.940 --> 00:32:42.290 line:80%
No matter what happens tomorrow,

00:32:42.290 --> 00:32:44.130 line:80%
you must not intervene.

00:32:47.020 --> 00:32:47.860 line:80%
Song,

00:32:48.980 --> 00:32:50.460 line:80%
do you think I'll win this bet?

00:33:32.050 --> 00:33:33.756 line:80%
This is the first Chief
of the demonic sect

00:33:34.420 --> 00:33:36.290 line:80%
in 200 years

00:33:36.290 --> 00:33:38.020 line:80%
to be tried at Qingque Sect.

00:33:39.020 --> 00:33:40.660 line:80%
Everyone, stay alert.

00:33:41.660 --> 00:33:43.013 line:80%
Guard against demonic sect members

00:33:43.660 --> 00:33:44.740 line:80%
attempting a rescue.

00:33:44.850 --> 00:33:45.700 line:80%
Yes.

00:33:56.370 --> 00:33:58.180 line:80%
A cup of tea in the morning

00:33:58.180 --> 00:33:59.700 line:80%
brings long life and blessings.

00:34:09.540 --> 00:34:10.540 line:80%
Zhao,

00:34:10.540 --> 00:34:12.290 line:80%
if you have something on your mind,

00:34:12.290 --> 00:34:13.660 line:80%
don't bottle it up.

00:34:13.660 --> 00:34:15.370 line:80%
As long as we can do it,

00:34:15.370 --> 00:34:16.810 line:80%
we will do it for you.

00:34:16.810 --> 00:34:18.220 line:80%
Yes, your mother is right.

00:34:21.370 --> 00:34:22.636 line:80%
I want to witness the execution.

00:34:24.180 --> 00:34:25.370 line:80%
Witness it?

00:34:29.890 --> 00:34:31.660 line:80%
I only want to see him one last time.

00:34:32.490 --> 00:34:33.700 line:80%
After it ends,

00:34:35.140 --> 00:34:36.410 line:80%
I'll return to Luoying Valley

00:34:36.780 --> 00:34:37.780 line:80%
with you two

00:34:38.740 --> 00:34:39.740 line:80%
and never see him again.

00:34:46.740 --> 00:34:47.780 line:80%
It's right to see him off.

00:34:50.540 --> 00:34:51.450 line:80%
I'll take you.

00:34:57.370 --> 00:34:58.210 line:80%
Lord Song.

00:35:00.140 --> 00:35:00.980 line:80%
Lord Yang.

00:35:02.580 --> 00:35:03.420 line:80%
Have you heard?

00:35:03.780 --> 00:35:04.620 line:80%
What?

00:35:04.930 --> 00:35:07.310 line:80%
Luoying Valley intends to take
Mu Qingyan for recuperation.

00:35:08.180 --> 00:35:09.540 line:80%
In my view, only by imprisoning him

00:35:09.540 --> 00:35:11.370 line:80%
in Siqi Sect is it fair.

00:35:12.330 --> 00:35:13.620 line:80%
Don't take offense.

00:35:14.290 --> 00:35:15.140 line:80%
Your sects

00:35:15.450 --> 00:35:17.180 line:80%
all have ties with this fiend.

00:35:17.700 --> 00:35:19.780 line:80%
Only Siqi Sect is impartial.

00:35:20.290 --> 00:35:21.620 line:80%
I must reason with Lord Qi.

00:35:27.540 --> 00:35:28.580 line:80%
Little skill,

00:35:29.540 --> 00:35:31.060 line:80%
but great ambition.

00:35:31.060 --> 00:35:32.580 line:80%
Impartial?

00:35:32.580 --> 00:35:34.410 line:80%
He only covets the Mu clan's

00:35:34.410 --> 00:35:36.810 line:80%
secret manuals and treasures.

00:35:36.810 --> 00:35:38.180 line:80%
Has he not considered

00:35:38.180 --> 00:35:40.450 line:80%
why I didn't insist
on detaining him at Guangtian Sect?

00:35:41.450 --> 00:35:44.620 line:80%
The Mu clan
has ruled Li Sect for 200 years.

00:35:44.620 --> 00:35:46.740 line:80%
Mu Qingyan is a hot potato.

00:35:47.540 --> 00:35:49.100 line:80%
Wherever he is held,

00:35:49.100 --> 00:35:50.850 line:80%
trouble will follow.

00:35:51.740 --> 00:35:52.580 line:80%
Father,

00:35:53.450 --> 00:35:55.580 line:80%
don't you find this strange?

00:35:55.580 --> 00:35:57.180 line:80%
Mu Qingyan was captured only days ago,

00:35:57.180 --> 00:35:58.859 line:80%
yet Nie Zhe
has already reclaimed Li Sect.

00:35:59.370 --> 00:36:00.740 line:80%
It's too fast.

00:36:04.220 --> 00:36:06.060 line:80%
Based on my hard-won experience

00:36:06.060 --> 00:36:08.490 line:80%
fighting the demonic sect for decades,

00:36:09.370 --> 00:36:10.660 line:80%
it's indeed suspicious.

00:36:16.060 --> 00:36:17.060 line:80%
Uncle Zhou.

00:36:24.100 --> 00:36:24.970 line:80%
Zhao?

00:36:28.490 --> 00:36:29.330 line:80%
Let's go.

00:36:30.740 --> 00:36:31.700 line:80%
You go ahead.

00:36:35.290 --> 00:36:36.550 line:80%
You are here to witness as well?

00:36:38.100 --> 00:36:39.290 line:80%
To see him off one last time.

00:36:40.660 --> 00:36:41.500 line:80%
That is fine.

00:36:43.580 --> 00:36:44.420 line:80%
Uncle Zhou,

00:36:45.620 --> 00:36:47.490 line:80%
I spoke rashly yesterday.

00:36:47.490 --> 00:36:48.930 line:80%
Please don't take it to heart.

00:36:50.100 --> 00:36:51.740 line:80%
Aunt often told me

00:36:51.740 --> 00:36:53.850 line:80%
that at Peiqiong Manor,

00:36:54.050 --> 00:36:56.090 line:80%
you taught her to write
and practice martial arts.

00:36:56.580 --> 00:36:59.290 line:80%
I wonder

00:37:00.240 --> 00:37:01.780 line:80%
what she was like there.

00:37:06.890 --> 00:37:08.630 line:80%
She was your fiancée.

00:37:09.010 --> 00:37:10.010 line:80%
Poor thing.

00:37:10.010 --> 00:37:11.140 line:80%
Her parents were gone,

00:37:11.620 --> 00:37:13.780 line:80%
leaving her and her brother behind.

00:37:31.330 --> 00:37:32.433 line:80%
This is the MoonLake,

00:37:32.444 --> 00:37:33.490 line:80%
created by the fourth lord

00:37:33.490 --> 00:37:35.930 line:80%
while walking by the lake with his wife.

00:37:36.330 --> 00:37:38.330 line:80%
It means two shadows by the lake,

00:37:38.810 --> 00:37:40.810 line:80%
two hearts in harmony under the moon.

00:37:42.660 --> 00:37:43.930 line:80%
Pingshu, what is wrong?

00:37:43.930 --> 00:37:45.850 line:80%
You grasp
even the hardest moves at once.

00:37:46.290 --> 00:37:48.450 line:80%
Why can't you master

00:37:48.649 --> 00:37:50.043 line:80%
such a simple move as the MoonLake?

00:37:53.850 --> 00:37:55.060 line:80%
MoonLake...

00:37:56.370 --> 00:37:57.210 line:80%
Pingshu,

00:37:57.890 --> 00:37:59.490 line:80%
Mother only pitied Cousin Min.

00:37:59.490 --> 00:38:00.930 line:80%
Why argue with her?

00:38:12.890 --> 00:38:14.076 line:80%
Let's break off the betrothal.

00:38:17.740 --> 00:38:19.220 line:80%
Zhou, take care.

00:38:25.140 --> 00:38:27.100 line:80%
Later, when war broke out,

00:38:27.100 --> 00:38:28.780 line:80%
she devoted herself
to eradicating fiends.

00:38:29.780 --> 00:38:31.290 line:80%
I seldom saw her again.

00:38:32.140 --> 00:38:32.980 line:80%
Uncle Zhou,

00:38:34.140 --> 00:38:36.220 line:80%
in Aunt's heart,

00:38:36.220 --> 00:38:38.370 line:80%
you were not without weight.

00:38:41.540 --> 00:38:42.380 line:80%
I know.

00:40:04.361 --> 00:40:15.021 line:80%
=Generation to Generation=

00:40:33.781 --> 00:40:38.191 line:80%
♪The breeze is gentle,
and spring is fair♪

00:40:38.756 --> 00:40:43.371 line:80%
♪I roam the rivers and hills
in the martial world♪

00:40:43.711 --> 00:40:48.276 line:80%
♪With a shining cup,
I drink with delight tonight♪

00:40:48.801 --> 00:40:53.101 line:80%
♪Free to wander in the world♪

00:40:56.046 --> 00:41:00.746 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:41:01.271 --> 00:41:05.561 line:80%
♪I rest beneath the stars' soft gleam♪

00:41:06.221 --> 00:41:10.251 line:80%
♪The night is calm, still as a stream♪

00:41:10.566 --> 00:41:15.691 line:80%
♪It washes away all judgment and scheme♪

00:41:16.266 --> 00:41:21.076 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:41:21.291 --> 00:41:25.461 line:80%
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

00:41:26.186 --> 00:41:30.121 line:80%
♪I freely roam in the world♪

00:41:30.621 --> 00:41:35.896 line:80%
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪

00:41:58.626 --> 00:42:03.756 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:42:04.121 --> 00:42:08.491 line:80%
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

00:42:08.756 --> 00:42:12.886 line:80%
♪I freely roam in the world♪

00:42:13.071 --> 00:42:18.646 line:80%
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪